data.text:
Name Lists for Boxes 1 through 13

National Archives Identifier 2123997

The Names List includes the names of visa and passport registration applicants, organizations or groups found in each folder of each box. The intension is to facilitate genealogical research, and every effort was made to capture as comprehensive a list as possible in order to include all names with case files and visa applications. The list will be updated as needed.

Notes:

File units and case files contained in file units are organized in alphabetical order.

FNU stands for First Name Unknown.

File unit titles are in bold type.

A name listed does not equate to a complete case file. The content of each case file or file unit varies for each person listed.

You can also download this Name Lists page as a PDF
